Input Optimization. AutoPrompt [autoprompt] introduced an automatic way of prompt generation given a specific task, such as fact retrieval. We generate our prompts as suggested by [autoprompt] on relation-specific training splits of \ourdataset{}. In Table (ref) the input optimization with AutoPrompts achieves notable improvements for {{2303.11082_FO0017||FO}}, e.g. hasReligion increased from {{2303.11082_FO0018||FO}} to {{2303.11082_FO0019||FO}}, citizenOf from {{2303.11082_FO0020||FO}} to {{2303.11082_FO0021||FO}}. There is no deterioration in any of the relations.